elem_dict.text: Advanced SettingsVisual-only modeEnable deep learning-based element extraction from visual information (app screenshots). Visual mode ignores app structure (DOM), and is useful when testing apps that use non-standard elements, such as video streaming apps and games.Skip app installation on deviceThis skips all installation/uninstallation on the device, using the app as-is-installed for all testing.
